    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's been garage-kept since day one. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. You won't find another one like this! Come check it out and see for yourself\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
