    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S represents a pinnacle of mechanical preservation. The 3.8L flat-six exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders with no evidence of bore scoring or IMS bearing degradation. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle with a short-throw shifter, delivering a visceral connection to the pavement. The Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) system remains factory-spec, offering impeccable damping and lateral stability. Every bushing is pliable, the rear main seal is bone-dry, and the factory-applied paint maintains its original depth and luster. This is an investment-grade example with zero deferred maintenance, retaining its razor-sharp throttle response and chassis rigidity.",
